title: Inteq Gaming

embed.description: ►About us We're a multi-gaming community that welcomes everbody! In the future we're probably going to run rosters in many awesome games. Also, we gonna make a lot of giveaways and fun events! _______________________________________________________________ ►We're active in following games Couner Strike:Global Offensive League of Legends (contact Yubinator, EUW) Black Desert Online Rocket League ...and many more!

body: We are planning on a big Gaming Community. If you want to you can join our League of Legends club. We will be creating a League of Legends roster soon. if you are Platinum or better, you can apply yourself on Steam or League of Legends, just hit me up! All you have to do is to add Yubinator on League of Legends. Have fun in our Community and check it out on Steam! (Weekly Giveaways in our Steam Group.)
